{"tid":1201391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中貿易戰 越南政府誓言打擊中國洗產地商品","createTime":"2019-06-11T04:21:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T15:35:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87d6577ba78176de219306d3651914742631c793","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"美中貿易戰未歇，防範中國企業為逃避美國懲罰性關稅而「洗產地」的不只台灣。越南海關 9 日透過政府網站發布聲明指出，將嚴加打擊非法使用「越南製造」標示的中國出口商品。<br />\n<br />\n「偽造產地和非法轉運商品的情形最常見於紡織業、農漁產品、磁磚、蜂蜜、鋼鐵、鋁和木製品」。越南海關指出，一些本地進口商將來自中國的商品以標示「越南製造」（Made in Vietnam）的包裝材料非法重新包裝，隨後申請越南產地證明，再依此證明將中國製商品銷往美國、歐洲和日本。<br />\n<br />\n越方舉一個遭美國海關揭發的案例說明：一家越南木製品製造商遭揭發進口中國貨、重新貼標，再出口至美國。<br />\n<br />\n越南海關已著手擬定流程，以改善對相關違法企業的鑑別能力和依法懲治。<br />\n<br />\n業界分析，越南是美中貿易戰的主要受惠國之一，一些企業正把供應鏈逐步自中國轉移至越南，以避免美國政府對中國商品施加的懲罰性關稅。美國是越南最大的出口市場。"},{"pid":"520f04bb6a9b43da975442fdb9310863a400bdbf","tid":1201391,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:26:49.000Z","msg":"一齊夾爆支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55d1f95b23a5b32a37899515c96cac318cb6a09","tid":1201391,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包圍網"},{"pid":"f6c21a5a04c594fe9c9cd683df83005d9732fe24","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"大既意思係 用越南避關稅<br />\n在支那整好晒,之後運去越南出口"},{"pid":"2dbe9f9adac1a6bf7a0bc5b2063c7f810745a55d","tid":1201391,"uid":246156,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:31:26.000Z","msg":"東南亞梗係想大陸死多兩錢重，今次貿易戰係佢地嘅商機<br />\n<br />\n點會睇你大陸佬，成個東南亞都想你支爆"},{"pid":"6fe1fec8f97c579301746d534416e4c0b1e5252a","tid":1201391,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"唔係話中國製造好威架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堂堂大國做乜要冒越南依D小國啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611b394f109ec1f7f12fe0d5fef9249c12a7bf02","tid":1201391,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:43:50.000Z","msg":"支那十幾億隻狗洗驚你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54cddf197dbceabdaf7e0eefcbbe3088f25dad3","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"0d609ddffadc51924dba45857a1bc36b9246098c","tid":1201391,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"好勤力咁捉，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=================<br />\n&bull;Packaging on Chinese goods were found to have been relabeled to avoid tariffs <br />\n&bull;Goods including textiles, fisheries and steel carried fake product-origin papers<br />\n&bull;Exporters have been moving production from China to Vietnam to avoid levies<br />\n&bull;Vietnam exports to the U.S. soared this year amid a spiralling trade war<br />\n&bull; Trump said he will slap new tariffs on China if Xi backs out of G20 meeting<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/06/10/10/wire-14594212-1560159854-87_634x422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F10%2Fwire-14594212-1560159854-87_634x422.jpg&h=1f83eb1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Hanoi has vowed to crack down on Chinese companies illegally using 'Made in Vietnam' labels on goods shipped to the U.S. to avoid high tariffs. Above, a Ted Baker shirt labelled 'Made in Vietnam' in a factory in Hanoi<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/06/10/17/14608908-7123627-image-a-25_1560183031010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F17%2F14608908-7123627-image-a-25_1560183031010.jpg&h=c2f71a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Garment factory workers stitching apparel in a factory in Hanoi. Exporters have started shifting production from China to Vietnam to avoid 25 per cent levies imposed by U.S. President Donald Trump on $200 billion worth of Chinese goods amid a spiraling trade war<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/06/10/17/14607406-7123627-image-a-22_1560182449974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F17%2F14607406-7123627-image-a-22_1560182449974.jpg&h=86d5f4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The trend has 'affected the reputation of Vietnamese businesses and goods', said Vietnam's Deputy Prime Minister Pham Binh Minh, said in a report published Sunday on the government website. Above, Landmark 81, Vietnam's tallest building, is seen in Ho Chi Minh city<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/05/15/11/13456646-7031507-A_Chinese_worker_adjusts_a_hydraulic_lift_at_a_factory_which_pro-a-29_1557915329199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F05%2F15%2F11%2F13456646-7031507-A_Chinese_worker_adjusts_a_hydraulic_lift_at_a_factory_which_pro-a-29_1557915329199.jpg&h=b881dada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A Chinese worker adjusts a hydraulic lift at a factory which produces construction machinery for export to many countries, including the US, in Jinan, in east China's Shandong province<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/06/10/17/14458060-7123627-President_Trump_says_he_ll_wait_to_put_tariffs_on_the_remainder_-a-23_1560182611752.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F17%2F14458060-7123627-President_Trump_says_he_ll_wait_to_put_tariffs_on_the_remainder_-a-23_1560182611752.jpg&h=26f46ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The U.S. President warned today he will slap huge new tariffs on China if his counterpart Xi Jinping doesn't show up for a planned face-to-face meeting later this month<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/06/06/15/14458056-7112405-image-a-11_1559832901919.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F06%2F06%2F15%2F14458056-7112405-image-a-11_1559832901919.jpg&h=9bfca5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Asked if a failure by President Xi Jinping to come to the summit would lead to tariffs kicking in on a further $300 billion in Chinese imports, Trump told CNBC television: 'Yes it would'<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/06/10/5894312616511947779/1024x576_MP4_5894312616511947779.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F5894312616511947779%2F1024x576_MP4_5894312616511947779.mp4&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=04aed9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/06/10/5894312616511947779/1024x576_MP4_5894312616511947779.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/06/06/388224710179833230/1024x576_MP4_388224710179833230.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F06%2F06%2F388224710179833230%2F1024x576_MP4_388224710179833230.mp4&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=21129c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/06/06/388224710179833230/1024x576_MP4_388224710179833230.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7123627/Hanoi-curb-fake-Made-Vietnam-goods-aimed-dodging-US-tariffs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-7123627%2FHanoi-curb-fake-Made-Vietnam-goods-aimed-dodging-US-tariffs.html&d=0xAgwAOhMzbM3o1MPcLVD36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=61b33fd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-7123627/Hanoi-curb-fake-Made-Vietnam-goods-aimed-dodging-US-tariffs.html</a>"},{"pid":"bd93f449a702384d2366198264854d73ef2c0f11","tid":1201391,"uid":189638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"蝦蝦霸霸咁多年，周邊嘅人都想支那死"},{"pid":"097a4793d0f3d7a4803be36aa1c1d43538e0c207","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03805e3f52c504dae588c54423904e7627b8bf8b","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210334633745f55ac6a26a9ef8e92eac94e33d17","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e363445532e94ae7df162135914adcd75977c0c2","tid":1201391,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}